<br>
The other thing I hope they make sure to code properly is how this will work with character transfers to different accounts.  When you transfer a character to another account you own, all of his items, gear, and platinum come with him.  I can see the POTENTIAL for a dupe exploit if the contents of these &quot;shared&quot; slots are brought over to a new account.  I doubt it would happen if the the account the character is transferred to already has characters with items in the shared slots, but I wouldn't be so sure if the character was transferred to an account with no existing toons.<br>
<br>
/shrug, we'll see... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yyidth>yyidth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 285<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/16/03 9:39 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Bank feature on test...</span><hr size=1> Wow, that is one excellent feature. <p>-- <br>
